<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 flex flex-col min-h-screen">

    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow">
        
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="bg-[#a51c30] text-white py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
             <!-- Background Pattern Overlay (Optional) -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]"></div>
            
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">SimTech Computers</h1>
                 <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-red-100 mb-8">Your Smart Tech, Sustainable Choice</p>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Intro Section -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    At <span class="font-bold text-[#a51c30]">SimTech Computers</span>, we believe great technology shouldn’t come with a heavy price for your wallet. We bring you bargain-priced, factory-refurbished IT clearance stock including Refurbished Laptops, Computers, Smartphones, Workstations, and more.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Each device is professionally tested, renewed, and certified, ensuring it performs just as efficiently as a new one but at a fraction of the cost. With over 17 years of expertise, <span class="font-bold text-[#a51c30]">Simtech Computers</span> has established itself as one of India’s most trusted remarketers of IT equipment.
                </p>
                 <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    Every refurbished product we sell contributes to a greener tomorrow — because for every asset reused, one less is manufactured.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

         <!-- What We Offer Grid -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">What We Offer</h2>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    
                    <!-- Card 1: Laptops -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-macbook-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Refurbished Laptops</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Explore an extensive range from Dell, HP, Lenovo, and Apple. Ex-corporate laptops backed by a 1-Year Warranty and 30-Day Replacement Policy.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 2: Computers -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-computer-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Refurbished Computers</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Business-grade machines optimized for durability and speed. Perfect for office or personal use, combining high performance with affordability.</p>
                    </div>

                     <!-- Card 3: Just The Box -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-cpu-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Just The Box</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Modular setup offering the system unit only. Use your existing peripherals for a flexible and cost-effective upgrade.</p>
                    </div>

                     <!-- Card 4: All-in-One -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-tv-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">All In One Desktops</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sleek, space-saving designs merging performance with elegance. Ideal for professionals valuing functionality and aesthetics.</p>
                    </div>

                     <!-- Card 5: Workstations -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Workstations</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">High processing power for creators and engineers. Built for 3D modeling, video editing, and demanding applications.</p>
                    </div>

                     <!-- Card 6: Mobiles -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#a51c30] mb-6">
                            <i class="ri-smartphone-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Refurbished Mobiles</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Top-brand smartphones tested and restored. Enjoy premium devices like iPhones with warranty and quality assurance.</p>
                    </div>
                     <!-- Card 7: New Devices -->
                     <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-gray-100 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 text-center">
                         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 mb-6 mx-auto">
                            <i class="ri-box-3-line text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">New Laptops, Computers & Mobiles</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Looking for brand-new devices? Simtech Computers also offers New Laptops, Computers, and Mobiles at prices you’ll love. Get the latest technology with full manufacturer warranty all under one roof.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

         <!-- Why Choose Us -->
         <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Why Choose SimTech Computers</h2>
                 
                 <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#a51c30] mb-2">70%</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Box Savings</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#a51c30] mb-2">1 Year</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Warranty</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#a51c30] mb-2">30 Day</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Replacement</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#a51c30] mb-2">4.8 <i class="ri-star-fill text-yellow-400 text-2xl align-bottom"></i></h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Customer Review</p>
                    </div>
                 </div>
            </div>
         </section>

         <!-- Comparison Table -->
         <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
             <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Others vs SimTech Computers</h2>
                 
                 <div class="overflow-x-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                     <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                         <thead>
                             <tr class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
                                 <th class="p-4 font-bold text-gray-700">Feature</th>
                                 <th class="p-4 font-bold text-gray-500">Other Sellers</th>
                                 <th class="p-4 font-bold text-[#a51c30] bg-red-50">SimTech Computers</th>
                             </tr>
                         </thead>
                         <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 text-sm">
                             <tr>
                                 <td class="p-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Product Testing</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-500">Basic or minimal checks</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium bg-red-50">Factory-tested and certified</td>
                             </tr>
                             <tr>
                                 <td class="p-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Warranty</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-500">3–6 months limited</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium bg-red-50">1-Year Warranty on all products</td>
                             </tr>
                             <tr>
                                 <td class="p-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Replacement Policy</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-500">Rarely offered</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium bg-red-50">30-Day Replacement Guarantee</td>
                             </tr>
                              <tr>
                                 <td class="p-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Pricing</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-500">High markups</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium bg-red-50">Up to 70% less than retail</td>
                             </tr>
                              <tr>
                                 <td class="p-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Environmental Impact</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-500">High carbon footprint</td>
                                 <td class="p-4 text-gray-900 font-medium bg-red-50">Sustainable reuse</td>
                             </tr>
                         </tbody>
                     </table>
                 </div>
             </div>
         </section>

         <!-- Sustainability CTA -->
         <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden">
             <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/wood-pattern.png')]"></div>
             <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Sustainability That Matters</h2>
                 <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                     We don’t just sell technology. We redefine how it’s consumed. Every Refurbished Laptop, Computer, or Smartphone you buy from us prevents electronic waste and minimizes carbon emissions. It’s a small decision that creates a big difference, both for you and the planet.
                 </p>
                 <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-[#a51c30] hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                     Shop Sustainable Tech
                 </a>
             </div>
         </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
